.home-image.position-relative.p-3.p-md-5.text-center.bg-image
    .col-md-6.p-lg-5.mx-auto.my-5
        .d-flex.justify-content-center.align-items-center.h-100
            %h1.display-1.text-white
                Track, Share & Improve

        .d-flex.justify-content-center.align-items-center.h-100.mb-2
            .col-md-12.col-12.mx-auto
                %h5.mb-8.lead.text-white
                    GymTracker is an easy-to-use gym tracker & workout log allowing you to track your workouts, follow your friends, and see what they're up to.
        .col-6.mx-auto.mb-5
            - if user_signed_in?
                = link_to 'Get Started', "dashboard", class: 'btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg btn-block border border-white bg-primary text-white'
            - else
                = link_to 'Get Started', "users/sign_in", class: 'btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg btn-block border border-white bg-primary text-white'
        %br
        %br

.bg-dark.text-white
    .bg-body-tertiary.me-md-3.pt-3.px-3.pt-md-5.px-md-5.text-center.overflow-hidden
        .my-3.p-3
            %h2.display-5
                %i{class: "fa-solid fa-list", style: "color: #009dff;"}
                Log your workouts 
            %p.lead Track each and every set you do, whether thats a dropset, to failure or even a bodyweight set.
        .bg-white.shadow-sm.mx-auto{style: "width: 400px; height: 300px; border-radius: 21px 21px 0 0;"}


